WEBVTT

00:00:07.204 --> 00:00:11.141
2021 is a crucial year in the fight
against climate change.

00:00:11.174 --> 00:00:13.744
According to the Paris Agreement
timetable, this year,

00:00:13.777 --> 00:00:18.382
governments must make key decisions
on updating their climate action plans.

00:00:18.415 --> 00:00:21.251
Are we on track to meet the goal
of limiting global warming

00:00:21.251 --> 00:00:23.487
to 1.5 degrees Celsius?

00:00:23.487 --> 00:00:26.490
There is good news and bad news,
and the details matter,

00:00:26.523 --> 00:00:28.225
